HEADWORD: Campylotropous
<hw>Cam`py*lot"ro*pous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/
curved + <?/ a turning.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Having the ovules
